---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
description: Eamonns Coffee Shop — sip stellar brews and read spacey stories.
---
<section class="hero">
  <h1>Welcome to Eamonns Cofee Shop</h1>
  <p>Small sips. Big universe. Hand-crafted posts brewed fresh.</p>
  <p><a class="button" href="/blog/">Explore the Blog</a></p>
  <figure class="emoji">☕✨</figure>
  <hr />
  <h2>Latest Posts</h2>
  <ul class="post-list">
  {% for post in collections.posts | slice(0,3) %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      <small> — {{ post.date | date("MMM d, yyyy") }}</small>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>



